name: CubeTEST
description:
CubeTEST

You're a small, lost cube travelling through cities to find home but... obstacles are blocking your way.

Currently. game offers:

  • 6 Levels,
  • 6 Skins,
  • Probably bugs,
  • ...and that's it, for now at least

I plan on updating this game by adding new levels, modes, features, etc.

Game is also open-source meaning you contribute to it. Code is avaible on github.

If you have any questions dm me on discord (Cnnn666#5460), or join discord server and ask there.

Side note: game should run on toaster
